strawbees.easingLabels: A label of a easing equation.
strawbees.getHexColorFromHSB:
Calculates the hexadecimal representation of a color from the `hue`,
`saturation` and `brightness` of that the color.
strawbees.getHexColorFromHSB|param|brigh: Brightness of the color ranging from `0` to `100`
strawbees.getHexColorFromHSB|param|hue: Hue of the color ranging from `0` to `100`
strawbees.getHexColorFromHSB|param|satur: Saturation of the color ranging from `0` to `100`
strawbees.getHexColorFromRGB:
Calculates the hexadecimal representation of a color from the amounts of
`red`, `green` and `blue` in that the color.
strawbees.getHexColorFromRGB|param|blue: Amount of blue in color ranging from `0%` to `100%`
strawbees.getHexColorFromRGB|param|green: Amount of green in color ranging from `0%` to `100%`
strawbees.getHexColorFromRGB|param|red: Amount of red in color ranging from `0%` to `100%`
strawbees.setContinuousServoSpeed:
Sets the speed of a continuous servo in a arbitrary range from `-100%` to
`100%`.
strawbees.setContinuousServoSpeed|param|: The continuous servo to set the speed to.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorHSB:
Sets the color of an individual neopixel by specifying the amount of
`hue`, `saturation` and `brightness` in the color. The amounts range from
`0%` to `100%`.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorHSB|param|brig: Brightness of the color ranging from `0%` to `100%`.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorHSB|param|hue: Hue of the color ranging from `0%` to `100%`.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorHSB|param|neop: Which neopixel to set the color.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorHSB|param|satu: Saturation of the color ranging from `0%` to `100%`.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorLabel: Sets the color of an individual neopixel by specifying the color by name.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorLabel|param|co: The name of the color from a list of color labels.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorLabel|param|ne: Which neopixel to set the color.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorRGB:
Sets the color of an individual neopixel by specifying the amount of
`red`, `green` and `blue` in the color. The amounts range from `0%` to
`100%`.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorRGB|param|blue: Amount of blue in color ranging from `0%` to `100%`.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorRGB|param|gree: Amount of green in color ranging from `0%` to `100%`.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorRGB|param|neop: Which neopixel to set the color.
strawbees.setNeopixelColorRGB|param|red: Amount of red in color ranging from `0%` to `100%`.
strawbees.setNeopixelsBrightness:
Sets the brightness of all the neopixels by specifying a value ranging
from `0%` to `100%`.
strawbees.setNeopixelsBrightness|param|b: Brightness of the neopixels from `0%` to `100%`.
strawbees.setServoAngle: Sets the position of a servo by specifying the angle (in degrees).
strawbees.setServoAngle|param|degrees: The angle to be set from `0째` to `180째`.
strawbees.setServoAngle|param|servoLabel: The servo to set the position to.
strawbees.transitionServoAngle:
Transtions the position of a servo to the angle (in degrees) over a
duration of time (in seconds). The "shape" of the transtion is specified
by choosing one of the easing functions by name.
strawbees.transitionServoAngle|param|deg: The angle to be set from `0째` to `180째`.
strawbees.transitionServoAngle|param|ser: The servo to set the position to.
strawbees.turnOffServo:
Turns a servo off so that no force will be applied and the horn can be
rotated manually. This saves battery.
strawbees.wave:
Samples the vale of a periodic wave function. The wave starts at the
beginning of the running time. It can be configured by specifying it's
length (in seconds), amplitude and offset.
strawbees.waveTypeLabels: A label of a wave type.
strawbees.wave|param|length: The length (or period) of the wave, in seconds.
